trans-unit.target: TEXT_CTSDKBCHARACTER2SUB1_00575_RECORDSYSTEM_000_050<tab><blip> Greetings, <var 2C ((<var 29 EB02 /var>)) (( )) 02 /var>. Thank you for agreeing to knock Thiuna into shape.
TEXT_CTSDKBCHARACTER2SUB1_00575_RECORDSYSTEM_000_100<tab><blip> Be kindly informed that your every action is currently being recorded. <buzz> Remember to smile.
TEXT_CTSDKBCHARACTER2SUB1_00575_RECORDSYSTEM_000_150<tab><blip> Glory be to Allag. Long may she endure.
TEXT_CTSDKBCHARACTER2SUB1_00575_RECORDSYSTEM_000_160<tab><blip> Water and nodes do not mix. As a precautionary measure, I must maintain a safe distance from amaro.
TEXT_CTSDKBCHARACTER2SUB1_00575_RECORDSYSTEM_000_200<tab><blip> Be advised that forced shutdowns may result in corrupted data. It is recommended that you perform regular backups.

TEXT_CTSDKBCHARACTER2SUB1_00575_RECORDSYSTEM_000_350<tab><blip> All data pertaining to <var 29 EB02 /var> has been encrypted under the Protect protocol. <buzz> Your personal information is safe with me.
